，它还发生了近 20 次的 M 级耀斑，如此频繁的爆发是不是有些不正常呢？ 其实这和当前太阳活动处于高年的大背景非常相符，高年的特点就是黑子数量多，可能发生的爆发活动多。昨天国家空间天气监测预警中心就针对可能出现的耀斑活动发布了黄色预警。 那么未来还会发生哪些空间天气事件？地球会不会发生地磁暴？ 国家空间天气监测预警中心会密切关注太阳的最新动态，及时为大家做好相关服务。太阳连续大爆发！X1.3 级、 X1.2 级、 X4.5 级耀斑三连暴"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8c0542df532d7f208c8c5b023b0731f6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655204806"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5OLYtunXm8wlEAMaCTEwNzg3ODY0MyCO/+WxBjAAOFZALXIJNjU1MjA0ODA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1715066039.329525", "card_id": "Q_655030325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 104}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "面临婚姻破裂时，如何公正地处理夫妻财产分割问题，确保双方的权益得到保障？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "婚姻破裂时，夫妻财产分割是必须要解决的问题，如何公正地处理夫妻财产分割问题？欢迎大家多多讨论～～相关问题已收录至「法律观察室」话题活动，欢迎参与回答，抽奖赢好礼～！法律观察室"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/70/v2-1c5f95b462a3a2a433fec4515748d542_1440w.avis?source=172ae18b&biz_tag=Post"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655030325"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5OLYtunXm8wlEAMaCTEwNzg0MDAyNiCFutyxBjAAOKoBQC5yCTY1NTAzMDMyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1715066039.331448", "card_id": "Q_654800516", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "要是自驾长途游，你会准备哪些零食和饮料？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-eb84eb343ebc97f1c160cf7683bf4948_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_